            <div class="card pillar-card h-100 p-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <i class="fas fa-hands-helping text-info"></i>
                    <h5 class="card-title mt-3">For Valued Beneficiaries</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Submit your request for support easily and securely. We are here to help you access the aid you need.</p>
                    <a href="/Account/Register" class="btn btn-info mt-3">Request Assistance</a>
